ComicInfo.Summary:
Deadpool teams up with Outlaw, Agent X, and Sandi Brandenburg to take down Black Swan! But will this foursome fight against their common foe, or against each other?
Deadpool is hired by one of the four winds (a leader of one of the four biggest gangs in the Japan) to kill another gang leader. He winds up killing all four winds. This gives him a quite the reputation. but someone isn't happy about it all.
